name: InterLocke
description:
Made for GMTK GameJam 2021:

A simple game prototype where you must keep your boat connected to the tractor. How far can you get?

There were dreams for so much more, but time is a harsh mistress.

Shout out to ma boi Lee for all that was contributed! 

Checkout the source here - https://github.com/AlexKnowles/InterLocke
